From rrosebru@mta.ca Fri May  5 16:03:23 2006 -0300
Subject: Re: Construction of a real closure
To: categories@mta.ca (categories)
Date: Fri, 5 May 2006 07:55:57 -0700 (PDT)
From: "John Baez" <baez@math.ucr.edu>
