From rrosebru@mta.ca Fri May 19 08:25:48 2006 -0300
Subject: Re: Hecke eigensheaves and KV 2-vectors
To: categories@mta.ca (categories)
Date: Thu, 18 May 2006 08:30:57 -0700 (PDT)
From: "John Baez" <baez@math.ucr.edu>
